  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency humanitarian assistance to the most vulnerable flood-affected people in Kurigram and Jamalpur districts of Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will be implemented jointly by a consortium led by Christian Aid (CA) with Helpage International (HAI) Bangladesh as technical partner and Dhaka Ahsania Mission (DAM) in Jamalpur district and Aid Commila (AC) in Kurigram district as local implementing partners.  DAM and AC will engage women-headed CSOs who are currently disaster risk management and climate change capacity building partners of Christian Aid under an initiative funded by UN Women.</narrative>
  </description>
